reports.title: Esquema
reports.query: CALL db.schema.visualization;

reports.title: Diámetro del grafo dirigido
reports.query:
MATCH (n)
RETURN 13
LIMIT 1

reports.title: Diámetro del grafo no dirigido
reports.query:
MATCH (n)
RETURN 8
LIMIT 1

reports.title: Vista general
reports.query:
MATCH (n:Airport | Country)-[r]-(m)
RETURN n, r, m
LIMIT 1000

reports.title: Top de centralidad
reports.query:
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN 'Degree' AS Medida, a.Degree AS Resultado, a.name AS Nodo
ORDER BY Resultado DESC LIMIT 1
UNION
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN 'Out Degree' AS Medida, a.Out_Degree AS Resultado, a.name AS Nodo
ORDER BY Resultado DESC LIMIT 1
UNION
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN 'PageRank' AS Medida, a.PageRank AS Resultado, a.name AS Nodo
ORDER BY Resultado DESC LIMIT 1
UNION
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN 'Betweenness' AS Medida, a.BetweennessCentrality AS Resultado, a.name AS Nodo
ORDER BY Resultado DESC LIMIT 1
UNION
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN 'Closeness' AS Medida, a.ClosenessCentrality AS Resultado, a.name AS Nodo
ORDER BY Resultado DESC LIMIT 1;

reports.title: Top de comunidad
reports.query:
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN 'Triangle count' AS Medida, a.triangleCount AS Resultado, a.name AS Nodo
ORDER BY Resultado DESC LIMIT 1
UNION
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN 'K-1 Coloring' AS Medida, COUNT(DISTINCT a.color) AS Resultado, 'N/A' AS Nodo
ORDER BY Resultado DESC LIMIT 1
UNION
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN 'Louvain' AS Medida, COUNT(DISTINCT a.louvain) AS Resultado, 'N/A' AS Nodo
ORDER BY Resultado DESC LIMIT 1
UNION
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN 'Label Propagation' AS Medida, COUNT(DISTINCT a.labelPropagation) AS Resultado, 'N/A' AS Nodo
ORDER BY Resultado DESC LIMIT 1
UNION
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN 'Strong Components' AS Medida, COUNT(DISTINCT a.stronglyConnected) AS Resultado, 'N/A' AS Nodo
ORDER BY Resultado DESC LIMIT 1;

reports.title: Mayores conexiones
reports.query:
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN a.name AS Aeropuerto, a.Degree AS Conexiones
ORDER BY Conexiones DESC
LIMIT 5;

reports.title: Mayores salidas
reports.query:
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN a.name AS Aeropuerto, a.Out_Degree AS Salidas
ORDER BY Salidas DESC
LIMIT 5;

reports.title: Locaciones de difícil acceso
reports.query:
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN a.name AS Aeropuerto, a.In_Degree AS Entradas
ORDER BY Entradas
LIMIT 5;

reports.title: Aeropuerto más popular
reports.query:
CALL {
    MATCH (a:Airport)
    RETURN a.PageRank AS PR
    ORDER BY PR DESC LIMIT 1
} WITH toFloat(PR) AS PR
MATCH (a:Airport)
WITH a, toFloat(a.PageRank) AS pr, PR
RETURN
    a.name AS Airport
ORDER BY a.PageRank DESC
LIMIT 1;

reports.title: Conexiones complejas
reports.query:
CALL {
    MATCH (a:Airport)
    RETURN a.PageRank AS PR
    ORDER BY PR DESC LIMIT 1
} WITH toFloat(PR) AS PR
MATCH (a:Airport)
WITH a, toFloat(a.PageRank) AS pr, PR
RETURN
    a.name AS Aeropuerto,
    toString(100 - ROUND(pr/PR, 2)) + '%' AS Dificultad
ORDER BY a.PageRank
LIMIT 5;

reports.title: Locaciones de transbordo
reports.query:
CALL {
    MATCH (a:Airport)
    RETURN a.BetweennessCentrality AS BT
    ORDER BY BT DESC LIMIT 1
} WITH toFloat(BT) AS BT
MATCH (a:Airport)
WITH a, toFloat(a.BetweennessCentrality) AS bt, BT
RETURN
    a.name AS Aeropuerto,
    toString(ROUND(bt/BT, 2)*100) + '%' AS Porcentaje
ORDER BY a.BetweennessCentrality DESC
LIMIT 5;

reports.title: Centros de distribución comercial
reports.query:
CALL {
    MATCH (a:Airport)
    RETURN a.ClosenessCentrality AS CT
    ORDER BY CT DESC LIMIT 1
} WITH toFloat(CT) AS CT
MATCH (a:Airport)
WITH a, toFloat(a.ClosenessCentrality) AS ct, CT
RETURN
    a.name AS Aeropuerto,
    toString(ROUND(ct/CT, 2)*100) + '%' AS Porcentaje
ORDER BY a.ClosenessCentrality DESC
LIMIT 5;

reports.title: Centros de alto tráfico
reports.query:
CALL {
    MATCH (a:Airport)
    RETURN a.BetweennessCentrality AS BT
    ORDER BY BT DESC LIMIT 1
} WITH toFloat(BT) AS BT
CALL {
    MATCH (a:Airport)
    RETURN a.ClosenessCentrality AS CT
    ORDER BY CT DESC LIMIT 1
} WITH toFloat(CT) AS CT, BT
MATCH (a:Airport)
WITH a,
    toFloat(a.BetweennessCentrality) AS bt,
    toFloat(a.ClosenessCentrality) AS ct,
    BT, CT
RETURN
    a.name AS Airport,
    toString(ROUND(bt/BT, 2)*100) + '%' AS Conecta,
    toString(ROUND(ct/CT, 2)*100) + '%' AS Distribuye
ORDER BY
    a.BetweennessCentrality DESC,
    a.ClosenessCentrality DESC,
    Airport
LIMIT 5;

reports.title: Grupos aeroportuarios
reports.query:
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN
    a.louvain AS Grupo,
    COLLECT(a.name) AS Miembros
ORDER BY Grupo;

reports.title: Alta frecuencia de viajes
reports.query:
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN a.name AS Aeropuerto, a.triangleCount AS Destinos
ORDER BY Destinos DESC
LIMIT 10;

reports.title: Segunda división aeroportuaria
Conteo de miembros
reports.query:
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN
    a.labelPropagation AS Agrupación,
    SUM(a.triangleCount) AS Total
ORDER BY Total DESC, Agrupación;

reports.title: Posibilidad de viajes redondos
Grupos con pactos internos
Cantidad de temáticas globales
reports.query:
MATCH (a:Airport)
RETURN COUNT(DISTINCT a.color) AS totalColores;
